{"id":71722,"date":"2017-03-08T00:00:00","date_gmt":"2017-03-08T00:00:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/2017\/03\/08\/financial-commission-successfully-participated-in-2017-ifx-expo-asia\/"},"modified":"2020-09-30T17:01:38","modified_gmt":"2020-09-30T17:01:38","slug":"financial-commission-successfully-participated-in-2017-ifx-expo-asia","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/2017\/03\/08\/financial-commission-successfully-participated-in-2017-ifx-expo-asia\/","title":{"rendered":"Financial Commission Successfully Participated in 2017 iFX Expo Asia","gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"text"}]},"content":{"rendered":"<p>March 7, 2017, Financial Commission, a leading External Dispute Resolution (EDR) organization, operated by FinaCom PLC, servicing online brokerages and technology providers within the financial services industry is pleased to announce its recent successful participation at the iFX EXPO Asia in Hong Kong.<\/p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-36487\" src=\"https:\/\/xcv.financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-work-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"asia-work\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-work-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-work-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-work-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-work.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/><\/td>\n<td>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Financial Commission took part in iFX EXPO Asia in Hong Kong on February 21<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">st<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> through the 23<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">rd<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> at the Hong Kong Convention and Exhibition Center, with over 80 exhibitors and sponsors and more than 2,500 attendees present.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our representatives met in person with event delegates and helped answer questions while increasing industry awareness of Financial Commission\u2019s efficient dispute resolution process and membership benefits.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition, there were over 30 industry speakers who participated in various panels and theme-focused workshops, including Andrew Ralich, a member of Financial Commission\u2019s Dispute Resolution Committee (DRC), among other distinguished industry figures.<\/span><\/p>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-36492\" src=\"https:\/\/xcv.financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-GREENBERG-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"asia-greenberg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-GREENBERG-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-GREENBERG-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-GREENBERG-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-GREENBERG.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/td>\n<td style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-36497\" src=\"https:\/\/xcv.financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-2-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"asia-2\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-2-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-2-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-2-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Anatoly Bulanov \u2013 FinaCom Head of Dispute Resolution Committee\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Michael Greenberg &#8211; FinaCom\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Board Member,\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">CEO Finance Magnates<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Artem Karpichenko \u2013\u00a0Senior Operation Officer<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Anatoly Bulanov \u2013 FinaCom Head of Dispute Resolution Committee\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\">Artem Karpichenko \u2013\u00a0Senior Operation Officer<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\">Lidia Bekenova &#8211; Senior Relationship Manager<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">During the event, at least 8 brokers indicated interest in applying for membership with the Financial Commission, reflecting an increase year-over-year compared to the 2016 iFX EXPO Asia in Hong Kong, as interest in client education and maintaining positive customer relationships remains of paramount importance.<\/span><\/p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-36493\" src=\"https:\/\/xcv.financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-RALICH-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"asia-ralich\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-RALICH-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-RALICH-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-RALICH.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" \/><\/td>\n<td style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-36498\" src=\"https:\/\/xcv.financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-team-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"asia-team\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-team-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-team-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/ASIA-team.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" \/><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Anatoly Bulanov \u2013 FinaCom Head of Dispute Resolution Committee\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Andrew Ralich \u2013 Co-Founder oneZero Financial,\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Anatoly Bulanov \u2013 FinaCom Head of Dispute Resolution Committee\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\">Lidia Bekenova &#8211; Senior Relationship Manager<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Commenting about the event participation, Financial Commission Chairman, Peter Tatarnikov said, \u201cWe are pleased to have exhibited at yet another successful event in Hong Kong at this year\u2019s iFX EXPO Asia and extend many thanks to our members and delegates at the event that showed support.\u201d<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201cAsia remains an important region for Financial Commission to support due to the high growth of new market entrants from mainland China, and an evolving regulatory landscape across ASEAN economies for brokers and trading technology developers.\u201d<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mr. Tatarnikov added: \u201cFinancial Commission is well positioned to accommodate demand from firms in Asia that want the benefits of providing their clients with fair and efficient dispute resolution by becoming members.\u201d<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To learn more about how Financial Commission provides companies and their clients with an effective dispute resolution channel visit FinancialCommission.org or contact us to learn more about membership requirements.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>March 7, 2017, Financial Commission, a leading External Dispute Resolution (EDR) organization, operated by FinaCom PLC, servicing online brokerages and technology providers within the financial services industry is pleased to announce its recent successful participation at the iFX EXPO Asia in Hong Kong. Financial Commission took part in iFX EXPO Asia in Hong Kong on [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"author":1,"featured_media":116917,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[6293,1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-71722","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-industry-events-participation","category-uncategorized"],"acf":[],"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"link","format":"url"}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/71722","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=71722"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/71722\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/116917"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=71722"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=71722"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=71722"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}